OL,4,Cjailed for child sexual abuse
OL,6,FA former Sea Cadets volunteer who
OL,7,Fsexually abused children over a six-
OL,8,Fyear period has been jailed.
OL,10,FPhillip Grove, 70 from Sheffield,
OL,11,Flived in Taunton when he carried out
OL,12,Fthe crimes in the 1990s during his
OL,13,Ftime as a volunteer.
OL,15,FHe was jailed for 22 years at Taunton
OL,16,FCrown Court on Friday 23 February
OL,17,Fafter being found guilty of 15 charges
OL,18,Flinked to non-recent sexual offences,
OL,19,Fincluding rape.
