OL,4,Cjailed for child sexual abuse
OL,6,FA jury found Grove guilty of two
OL,7,Fcounts of rape, 10 counts of indecency
OL,8,Fwith a child and three counts of
OL,9,Findecent assault.
OL,11,FThey heard how, in the 90s while
OL,12,Fholding the position of Chief Petty
OL,13,FOfficer at a Sea Cadet group, he raped
OL,14,Fone of the victims, sexually assaulted
OL,15,Fanother and was indecent in front of
OL,16,Ftwo other victims.
OL,18,FIn September 2020, one of the victims
OL,19,Freported what had happened to her and
OL,20,Fthe other children to police and an
OL,21,Finvestigation into Grove was launched.
