OL,6,FOne of the victims said in a statement
OL,7,Fread out in court: "For almost 30
OL,8,Fyears, I have lived in constant shame.
OL,9,FShame which I have owned but it was
OL,10,Fnever actually mine to own.
OL,12,F"The whole of my adult life has been
OL,13,Fovercast in shadow, which I have never
OL,14,Fbeen able to shake off... A part of
OL,15,Fme, who I am, was taken away from me
OL,16,Fby Phillip Grove.
