OL,6,F"My days are plagued by the memories
OL,7,Fof what happened and the nights I
OL,8,Fmanage to get sleep, I am haunted by
OL,9,Fnightmares of both the incidents and
OL,10,FPhillip himself."
OL,12,FIn a letter to the judge, one victim
OL,13,Fsaid she felt "worthless" after what
OL,14,FGrove had done to her and described
OL,15,FGrove as a "sick, sick man".
OL,17,FGrove was arrested in March 2021 for
OL,18,Fthe offences and on Friday 8 December
OL,19,Flast year he was unanimously found
OL,20,Fguilty for 15 of the 16 charges put to
OL,21,Fhim.
