OL,6,FPresiding Judge Cullum referred to
OL,7,FGrove as a "dangerous individual".
OL,9,F"You are a self-centred, dishonest and
OL,10,Fcallous individual who has shown no
OL,11,Fremorse," he added.
OL,13,FSpeaking following the sentencing,
OL,14,Finvestigating officer Detective
OL,15,FConstable Becky Norton said: "All four
OL,16,Fvictims have been incredibly brave
OL,17,Fthroughout the process and have
OL,18,Fexhibited exceptional courage.
