OL,6,F"The Sea Cadets have been very
OL,7,Fsupportive of our investigation and,
OL,8,Fupon being contacted in October 2020,
OL,9,Ftheir safeguarding team conducted an
OL,10,Finternal investigation to gather
OL,11,Fnecessary information to support our
OL,12,Fenquiries.
OL,14,F"I hope this result reassures other
OL,15,Fvictims of non-recent sexual offences
OL,16,Fthat it is never too late to report a
OL,17,Fcrime to police. I would like to thank
OL,18,Fthe victims once again for showing
OL,19,Fincredible strength in coming forward."
